Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.68,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(968,16)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:53.61,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}这种事情 可不能大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.36,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(964,22)}Good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:59.38,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}最后的选择是心中永远的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:02.22,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}无关胜负 说得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:02.89,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(968,16)}I know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:05.08,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}能够鼓励我 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:05.78,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(968,16)}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.96,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}最后还是要靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.74,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不做好觉悟可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:12.94,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}这是深得我心的小建议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:18.67,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}道理有时并不管用 进退两难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:23.68,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}顺其自然或许更好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:27.23,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}命运不停轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.81,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我们就在此一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:35.66,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}还没做好心理准备稍等一下好么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:38.60,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}闪耀吧 这里最强
